42
00:06:21.198 --> 00:06:23.281
- Vær så god.
- Takk.


43
00:06:23.364 --> 00:06:24.989
Forsiktig. Kaffen er varm.

44
00:06:27.364 --> 00:06:28.614
Du har sukker der.

45
00:06:29.364 --> 00:06:30.364
Takk.

46
00:06:34.406 --> 00:06:35.406
Faen.

47
00:06:40.489 --> 00:06:41.656
Ana!

48
00:06:44.989 --> 00:06:46.323
Din jævla kjerring.

49
00:06:46.906 --> 00:06:48.031
Det er stengt.

50
00:06:48.156 --> 00:06:51.823
